Class CommandImpl

java.lang.Object
fr.istic.aco.editor.command.CommandImpl
Direct Known Subclasses:
Copy, Cut, Deletion, Insertion, Paste, Selection
public class CommandImpl extends Object
Base class for all command implementations in the editor. Commands encapsulate actions to be executed on the engine.
